edu.umn.nlpengine

Interface LabelIndex<T extends Label>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of label that this label index contains.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLabelIndex, DistinctLabelIndex, StandardLabelIndex

    public LabelIndex<T extends Label>

    A collection of labels ordered by their location in text. By default sorts by ascending TextRange.getStartIndex and then ascending TextRange.getEndIndex.

    See Also:
    TextRange.getStartIndex, TextRange.getEndIndex
